headline.print_headline: Would-Be Moldova Election Kingmaker Flees Country Ahead of Sunday Polls
headline.main: Would-Be Moldova Election Kingmaker Flees Country Ahead of Sunday Polls

lead_paragraph: A would-be kingmaker in elections in Moldova, millionaire dark horse candidate Renato Usatii, said on Friday he had fled to Russia fearing arrest after his party was excluded from the vote in a move likely to embolden pro-European rivals.
